-- Deutsche Bank May Sell India Credit Card Portfolio, Economic Times Reports
-- B y   T h e o   M u l l e n
-- 2010-11-02T01:50:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/deutsche-may-sell-india-credit-card-unit-economic-times-says.html
Deutsche Bank is negotiating to sell
its credit card portfolio in India, the Economic Times reported,
citing sources it did not identify.  The bank has about 350,000 active card users in the
country, the newspaper said. Yes Bank and IndusInd Bank are
among the possible buyers, the Times said. Neither bank would
comment on the report, the newspaper said.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Theo Mullen at 
 tmullen11@bloomberg.net  